SubjectKuper Island Indian Reserve No. 7 (also known as Penelakut Island Indian Reserve No.7) (British Columbia) ** Revocation of a Designation for leasing purposes **
PrecisOrder accepting a REVOCATION OF DESIGNATION for leasing purposes of approximately 308.37 hectares (762 acres) of land on KUPER ISLAND INDIAN RESERVE NO. 7 (also known as PENELAKUT ISLAND INDIAN RESERVE NO. 7), in BRITISH COLUMBIA.
